{
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-0r.ancient": "A Shinigami come to take my soul?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-0r.next": "Complain",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-1r.char": "I'm not here to kill you, but you're killing way too many people! That's making my job way harder than it should be!",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-1r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-2r.ancient": "You only care about your workload?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.0-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-0r.ancient": "Aren't you supposed to do your job?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-0r.next": "Complain",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-1r.char": "There are so many souls around here that it's almost impossible to do that!",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-1r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-2r.char": "Could you at least lend me some boats?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-2r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-3r.ancient": "I'm not lending you a boat. Go away.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-0r.ancient": "Slacking off again?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-0r.next": "Complain",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-1r.char": "I'm not slacking off! First off, the problem of dead souls is all your fault.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-1r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-2r.ancient": "Sounds like an excuse to me.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-0r.ancient": "It's the Master of Slacking again.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-0r.next": "Complain",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-1r.char": "What's up with that title? Is there a [red]Shrine Maiden[/red] behind me?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-1r.next": "Lecture",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-2r.char": "In any case, whatever your experiments are, they aren't my concern.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-2r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-3r.char": "But your conduct with other people, especially your creations, need a lot of work.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-3r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-4r.char": "You keep getting 'unwanted' visitors right? That's because your only solution is to kill them, rather than asking why they climbed up in the first place.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-4r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-5r.char": "Keep letting it drift, and not only will your bad karma pile, but so will the grudges against you. That won't end prettily.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-5r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-6r.ancient": "Are you done yet?",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-6r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-7r.char": "Opps! Seems I caught Eiki's habit...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-7r.next": "Continue",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-8r.ancient": "Unfortunately, I don't have time to be lectured by a lazy Shinigami.",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.3-attack": "Both"
}